f\colon\mathbb R\to\mathbb R
a_1,a_2,a_3,\cdots,a_n\in\mathbb R.
f(x)=a_1\sin x+a_2\sin2x+a_3\sin3x+\cdots+a_n\sin nx,
 |f(x)|\le|\sin x|\quad \forall x\in \mathbb{R}
|a_1+2a_2+3a_3+\cdots+na_n|\le1
x
\sin x\neq 0
\left|\sum_{j=1}^na_j\frac{\sin(jx)}{\sin x}\right|\leq 1
x\to 0
\left|\sum_{j=1}^nja_j\frac{\sin(jx)}{jx}\frac x{\sin x}\right|\leq 1,
\left|\sum_{j=1}^nja_j\right|\leq 1,
